verificar si lo tienes configurado
ls -l ~/.msmtprc

y si no lo hay 

nano ~/.msmtprc

defaults
auth on
tls on
tls_trust_file /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
account gmail
host smtp.gmail.com
port 587
from tu_correo@gmail.com
user tu_correo@gmail.com
password xxxx  xxx xxx xxx
logfile ~/.msmtp.log

